      <title>英国央行维持利率不变后英镑触及 2022 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/pound-hits-highest-since-march-2022-after-boe-holds-rates-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国央行维持利率稳定并表示不会急于放松政策后，英镑兑美元升至两年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/pound-hits-highest-since-march-2022-after-boe-holds-rates-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:10:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行明年将削减 1000 亿英镑债券投资组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-to-reduce-bond-portfolio-by-100-billion-over-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行将继续维持削减债券资产负债表的步伐，这一决定可能会影响财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯在即将到来的预算中拥有多少财政火力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-to-reduce-bond-portfolio-by-100-billion-over-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:09:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行承诺采取渐进式宽松政策并决定维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-vows-gradual-approach-to-easing-as-rates-held-in-8-1-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行警告投资者，其不会急于放松货币政策，决定不会连续第二次下调借贷成本，等待通胀压力消退的进一步迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/boe-vows-gradual-approach-to-easing-as-rates-held-in-8-1-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
